Introduction

Dayoung is a member of the girl group Cosmic Girls/WJSN and she represents the Taurus sign in the groups concept. Seola, Dayoung, Exy, Eunseo, Cheng Xiao, Soobin, and Yeoreum are in YTeen which is the Starship unit with Monsta X. She was a contestant on K-Pop Star 1.

She debuted as a member of WJSN on February 25, 2016 and the sub unit WJSN Chocome on October 7, 2020.
